1
00:01:25,800 --> 00:01:30,800
"Sammy's Children's Day"

2
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:34,000
(Episode 9)

3
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:36,120
Xia Liuyi.

4
00:01:38,519 --> 00:01:40,519
The truth is, I don't have
some emotional disorder.

5
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:45,640
I just...

6
00:01:48,519 --> 00:01:49,519
like you.

7
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:50,840
I like you.

8
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:52,680
I really like you.

9
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,560
I... I'm sorry.

10
00:02:24,599 --> 00:02:26,159
I have to get to work.

11
00:02:29,199 --> 00:02:30,199
I forgot my glasses.

12
00:05:13,639 --> 00:05:14,639
I'm back.

13
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:17,680
I'm back.

14
00:05:26,319 --> 00:05:27,319
I'm back.

15
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:49,040
Brother Liuyi.

16
00:05:51,519 --> 00:05:52,519
Fatty Seven.

17
00:05:53,519 --> 00:05:55,040
I've got this pretty boy here.

18
00:05:55,519 --> 00:05:57,240
He seems to know you well,

19
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,839
but he won't admit it.

20
00:05:59,079 --> 00:06:01,560
So I thought I'd call and ask.

21
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:03,680
What the hell are you talking about?

22
00:06:05,079 --> 00:06:06,079
Forgot him already?

23
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:08,079
You're a busy man, Brother Liuyi.

24
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,240
No worries.

25
00:06:09,279 --> 00:06:11,920
I'll just ask him more... thoroughly.

26
00:06:38,279 --> 00:06:41,519
Hey pretty boy, how long
have you been with Liuyi?

27
00:06:42,399 --> 00:06:43,959
I don't know what you're talking about.

28
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:46,000
You don't, huh?

29
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:48,959
I heard you two are quite close.

30
00:06:49,639 --> 00:06:51,519
Who knew he had a type?

31
00:06:53,959 --> 00:06:55,199
You've got it all wrong.

32
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:57,920
I know Mr. Xia,

33
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:01,319
but I'm just his financial advisor.

34
00:07:08,639 --> 00:07:09,776
You really have the wrong person.

35
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:11,079
We aren't close.

36
00:07:13,079 --> 00:07:14,119
Xia Liuyi,

37
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:16,240
your pretty boy still won't talk.

38
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:18,879
Guess you didn't treat him well enough.

39
00:07:19,079 --> 00:07:21,639
Maybe I should show him some kindness.

40
00:07:26,519 --> 00:07:29,279
How about showing some sincerity

41
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:31,839
if you want your sweetheart back?

42
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:39,360
One finger,

43
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:41,639
or one storefront. What do you say?

44
00:07:46,199 --> 00:07:48,560
He's just an accountant
who crunches numbers.

45
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,480
He's not worth that much.

46
00:07:51,519 --> 00:07:52,519
To be honest,

47
00:07:52,759 --> 00:07:55,000
he's the most useless guy I've got.

48
00:07:55,319 --> 00:07:57,680
Stop wasting my time.

49
00:08:05,639 --> 00:08:07,600
That damn cop wouldn't lie to me.

50
00:08:12,959 --> 00:08:13,959
Fine.

51
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,079
This is getting interesting.

52
00:08:19,639 --> 00:08:20,639
Kid,

53
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:23,399
either you're completely worthless to him,

54
00:08:23,639 --> 00:08:26,560
or you're everything.

55
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:30,839
Seven.
Do we still cut him?

56
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:34,039
Just beat him.

57
00:08:39,759 --> 00:08:41,559
Fatty Seven kidnapped He Chusan.

58
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,519
Check every single one

59
00:08:46,039 --> 00:08:49,159
of Fatty Seven's hideouts.

60
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:53,720
I don't care if you have to
turn the whole city upside down,

61
00:08:54,639 --> 00:08:56,919
find him!

62
00:09:11,279 --> 00:09:12,678
Still won't admit it, huh?

63
00:09:12,679 --> 00:09:13,679
Pretty boy.

64
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:21,960
Beat him!

65
00:09:22,639 --> 00:09:23,639
Die!

66
00:09:24,759 --> 00:09:25,480
Mr. Xie.

67
00:09:25,481 --> 00:09:27,201
One of Fatty Seven's guys
kidnapped someone.

68
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,520
The victim's record is clean.

69
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:30,600
He has no history with Fatty Seven.

70
00:09:30,759 --> 00:09:31,759
No connection at all.

71
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:33,000
It's strange.

72
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:37,600
Who did they take?

73
00:09:40,207 --> 00:09:41,200
[At the] Kwai Chung warehouse.

74
00:09:41,201 --> 00:09:42,279
He Chusan.

75
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:04,279
He Chusan and Xia Liuyi.

76
00:10:04,519 --> 00:10:05,720
What's going on?

77
00:10:06,879 --> 00:10:08,639
He Chusan and Xia Liuyi...

78
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:10,799
Mr. Xie.

79
00:10:11,039 --> 00:10:12,120
It's me.

80
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:14,200
I'm here to deliver your gift.

81
00:10:14,279 --> 00:10:15,279
I...

82
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:18,960
He Chusan.

83
00:10:36,879 --> 00:10:37,959
What are you trying to say?

84
00:10:45,759 --> 00:10:48,320
Don't play dumb with me, Mr. Xie.

85
00:10:52,919 --> 00:10:53,919
Listen.

86
00:10:58,279 --> 00:11:01,519
Xia Liuyi and Fatty Seven
are going to war tonight.

87
00:11:01,879 --> 00:11:03,558
While they're busy killing each other,

88
00:11:03,559 --> 00:11:05,240
you can swoop in and take the credit.

89
00:11:05,639 --> 00:11:08,120
So get your men ready

90
00:11:08,559 --> 00:11:09,679
to make the bust.

91
00:11:11,159 --> 00:11:12,159
What war?

92
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:16,080
And what does He Chusan
have to do with this?

93
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:21,559
Impressive, Mr. Xie.

94
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:23,759
You're already getting intel.

95
00:11:25,639 --> 00:11:26,799
He Chusan

96
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:29,960
is Xia Liuyi's lover.

97
00:11:31,799 --> 00:11:32,839
Lover.

98
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:34,559
Do you understand what that means?

99
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,320
It's just like...

100
00:11:37,799 --> 00:11:39,519
the relationship between you and me.

101
00:11:41,759 --> 00:11:42,798
I pulled some strings

102
00:11:42,799 --> 00:11:44,679
to leak that info to Fatty Seven.

103
00:11:45,639 --> 00:11:49,038
Imagine how excited he must be.

104
00:11:49,039 --> 00:11:49,919
Lu Guangming,

105
00:11:49,920 --> 00:11:51,320
who gave you permission to do that?

106
00:11:55,679 --> 00:11:57,479
Mr. Xie,

107
00:11:57,480 --> 00:11:59,320
I'm trying to help you.

108
00:12:00,279 --> 00:12:01,319
To close this case,

109
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:04,200
you need Liuyi and Fatty Seven.

110
00:12:07,759 --> 00:12:09,600
I've even got the charges ready.

111
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:12,878
Two gang bosses murdering an inspector,

112
00:12:12,879 --> 00:12:14,479
a bloody turf war,

113
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:16,758
all taken down by the OCTB's finest.

114
00:12:16,759 --> 00:12:17,759
When that happens,

115
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:19,558
whatever evidence you need,

116
00:12:19,559 --> 00:12:21,519
or any old cold cases you want to reopen,

117
00:12:21,799 --> 00:12:24,159
it'll be yours with a single word.

118
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:27,638
I want real evidence!

119
00:12:27,639 --> 00:12:28,919
I want lawful arrests,

120
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:31,039
not these underhanded tactics

121
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,878
that treat lives like garbage!

122
00:12:32,879 --> 00:12:34,878
You're going to get an innocent
citizen killed!

123
00:12:34,879 --> 00:12:35,879
Don't you realize that?

124
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:41,480
Innocent?

125
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:45,839
The moment he got involved with Liuyi,

126
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:47,399
he stopped being innocent.

127
00:12:50,919 --> 00:12:51,919
Xie Jiahua,

128
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:57,240
drop the useless sense of justice.

129
00:13:00,672 --> 00:13:05,233
This is your best shot.

130
00:13:17,279 --> 00:13:18,279
Get out of the car.

131
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:51,759
Aren't you going to answer?

132
00:13:51,760 --> 00:13:52,839
If I stay indifferent,

133
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:54,320
he won't dare to act rashly.

134
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:55,678
But if he knows I care about Chusan,

135
00:13:55,679 --> 00:13:56,919
he'll never let go.

136
00:13:57,279 --> 00:13:58,359
He'd probably cut off his limbs

137
00:13:58,360 --> 00:13:59,919
just to threaten me.

138
00:14:10,679 --> 00:14:11,200
Boss,

139
00:14:11,279 --> 00:14:12,720
Liuyi still isn't picking up.

140
00:14:13,679 --> 00:14:15,240
He won't learn until he sees a coffin.

141
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,399
An accountant, right?

142
00:14:24,879 --> 00:14:26,840
The most useless lackey, huh?

143
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:29,320
Keep beating him!

144
00:14:42,480 --> 00:14:44,000
Boss, we found him!

145
00:14:45,679 --> 00:14:46,159
Where?

146
00:14:46,160 --> 00:14:47,680
An abandoned warehouse in North Point.

147
00:14:47,879 --> 00:14:48,480
Go get the men.

148
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:49,600
I'm heading there now.

149
00:14:49,601 --> 00:14:50,919
Are you crazy?

150
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:53,000
The police are looking for you everywhere.

151
00:14:53,080 --> 00:14:54,798
This is probably a trap.

152
00:14:54,799 --> 00:14:55,799
It's too dangerous.

153
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:57,480
Let me go find the kid for you, okay?

154
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:59,240
I have to go, even if it is a trap.

155
00:14:59,519 --> 00:15:00,360
This is the only lead

156
00:15:00,361 --> 00:15:01,479
I have on He Chusan.

157
00:15:01,480 --> 00:15:02,480
Xia Liuyi!

158
00:15:03,639 --> 00:15:05,320
You're the head of the gang.

159
00:15:05,799 --> 00:15:07,679
What happens to us if
something happens to you?

160
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:19,159
I can't lose him again.

161
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:28,519
Go back to the office.

162
00:15:30,360 --> 00:15:31,719
If anything happens to me,

163
00:15:31,720 --> 00:15:33,000
you take charge.

164
00:15:37,480 --> 00:15:38,759
Let's kill them!

165
00:16:34,279 --> 00:16:35,320
He Chusan!

166
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:07,000
Xia Liuyi!

167
00:17:09,039 --> 00:17:10,039
Drop the knife!

168
00:17:10,519 --> 00:17:11,240
Or else,

169
00:17:11,480 --> 00:17:12,480
I'll kill him right now!

170
00:17:17,759 --> 00:17:18,759
Boss Xia,

171
00:17:19,119 --> 00:17:20,559
so high and mighty...

172
00:17:21,039 --> 00:17:22,559
and yet here you are, in my hands.

173
00:17:25,039 --> 00:17:26,039
Zheng Wu,

174
00:17:26,720 --> 00:17:28,000
we can talk about this.

175
00:17:29,480 --> 00:17:30,840
Whatever Fatty Seven promised you,

176
00:17:32,119 --> 00:17:33,559
I can double it.

177
00:17:34,960 --> 00:17:36,720
Look at Brother Liuyi, all anxious.

178
00:17:37,039 --> 00:17:38,679
Offering terms before the
negotiation even starts?

179
00:17:38,680 --> 00:17:40,839
You've already lost.

180
00:17:43,200 --> 00:17:44,200
Zheng Wu,

181
00:17:45,359 --> 00:17:47,119
my patience is wearing thin.

182
00:17:48,480 --> 00:17:50,000
While you still have a choice,

183
00:17:50,160 --> 00:17:51,799
I suggest you take the deal.

184
00:17:53,079 --> 00:17:55,000
I'm a simple man.

185
00:17:55,359 --> 00:17:57,359
I want you on your knees.

186
00:18:00,359 --> 00:18:01,119
What?

187
00:18:01,240 --> 00:18:02,240
Not interested?

188
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:06,720
Then the guy inside is as good as dead.

189
00:18:07,960 --> 00:18:08,960
Fine.

190
00:18:11,200 --> 00:18:12,200
I'll do it.

191
00:18:15,119 --> 00:18:16,839
Kneel! Do it!

192
00:18:17,200 --> 00:18:18,200
Get on your knees!

193
00:18:20,559 --> 00:18:21,599
Hurry up!

194
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:23,119
I'm waiting!

195
00:18:23,880 --> 00:18:25,839
I said kneel!

196
00:18:26,279 --> 00:18:27,799
Did you hear me?

197
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:30,000
Kneel!

198
00:18:30,920 --> 00:18:32,160
Kneel!

199
00:18:50,960 --> 00:18:51,960
Boss!

200
00:18:52,079 --> 00:18:53,079
We're here!

201
00:18:53,640 --> 00:18:54,640
I'll leave this to you.

202
00:18:56,960 --> 00:18:57,480
Don't move!

203
00:18:57,960 --> 00:18:58,960
Chusan!

204
00:18:59,559 --> 00:19:00,559
Chusan!

205
00:19:02,559 --> 00:19:03,559
Chusan!

206
00:19:08,279 --> 00:19:09,279
He Chusan!

207
00:19:10,039 --> 00:19:11,039
He Chusan!

208
00:19:12,039 --> 00:19:13,200
Where are you?

209
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:15,039
He Chusan!

210
00:19:15,160 --> 00:19:16,160
Boss.

211
00:19:20,119 --> 00:19:20,559
Ahao.
Boss.

212
00:19:22,119 --> 00:19:23,119
Give me my phone.

213
00:19:39,599 --> 00:19:40,599
Seven.

214
00:19:43,480 --> 00:19:45,480
My men had a run-in with Zheng Wu.

215
00:19:46,160 --> 00:19:47,798
But he pulled a gun first,

216
00:19:47,799 --> 00:19:49,119
breaking the rules of the street.

217
00:19:50,559 --> 00:19:51,559
I'll take the blame too.

218
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:53,320
I should've kept my men in check.

219
00:19:55,880 --> 00:19:57,120
How do you want to settle this?

220
00:19:57,839 --> 00:19:58,839
Name your price.

221
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:00,719
That depends on how much

222
00:20:00,720 --> 00:20:02,480
sincerity you have, Liuyi.

223
00:20:03,160 --> 00:20:04,480
A year's worth of our shipments.

224
00:20:05,720 --> 00:20:07,039
Did I hear that right?

225
00:20:07,480 --> 00:20:08,480
That's all?

226
00:20:09,039 --> 00:20:10,039
Let him go,

227
00:20:10,400 --> 00:20:11,480
and I'll deliver it myself.

228
00:20:13,039 --> 00:20:14,279
That's not nearly enough.

229
00:20:14,599 --> 00:20:15,720
Too stingy.

230
00:20:19,799 --> 00:20:21,319
The two biggest clubs in Mong Kok.

231
00:20:22,319 --> 00:20:23,319
They're yours.

232
00:20:24,640 --> 00:20:26,240
Still not enough.

233
00:20:28,039 --> 00:20:31,400
How about your gang's old ancestral hall?

234
00:20:36,720 --> 00:20:37,720
Fine.

235
00:20:39,200 --> 00:20:40,200
You've got a deal.

236
00:20:40,640 --> 00:20:41,640
Spoken like a man.

237
00:20:42,559 --> 00:20:44,599
He's at the ferry terminal.

238
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:45,640
Oh, by the way,
he's wearing a bomb.

239
00:20:46,880 --> 00:20:48,000
Better hurry, Boss Xia.

240
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:50,000
The ferry terminal.

241
00:20:50,640 --> 00:20:51,119
Go! Now!

242
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:52,960
Got it!

243
00:20:55,920 --> 00:20:56,920
He Chusan!

244
00:20:58,640 --> 00:20:59,640
Kid!

245
00:21:03,039 --> 00:21:03,759
He Chusan!

246
00:21:03,760 --> 00:21:05,039
This place is huge.

247
00:21:05,559 --> 00:21:06,640
Kid!

248
00:21:07,759 --> 00:21:08,759
He Chusan!

249
00:21:10,240 --> 00:21:11,240
Check over there!

250
00:21:11,559 --> 00:21:12,559
He Chusan!

251
00:21:13,279 --> 00:21:14,599
Kid!

252
00:21:15,839 --> 00:21:16,839
He Chusan!

253
00:21:17,880 --> 00:21:19,200
Damn it.

254
00:21:20,559 --> 00:21:22,039
I should never have met him.

255
00:21:26,160 --> 00:21:27,480
Make a movie for me.

256
00:21:28,480 --> 00:21:29,720
Write a story for me.

257
00:21:37,640 --> 00:21:38,640
Love

258
00:21:40,079 --> 00:21:41,359
is what happens

259
00:21:42,319 --> 00:21:44,640
when someone risks everything
to save another person.

260
00:21:50,680 --> 00:21:52,119
I have a gift for you.

261
00:22:02,160 --> 00:22:03,640
He Chusan,

262
00:22:13,720 --> 00:22:14,839
do you like it?

263
00:22:20,720 --> 00:22:21,720
I do.

264
00:22:26,039 --> 00:22:27,959
I don't care what happens to other thugs,

265
00:22:27,960 --> 00:22:29,380
but I can't be
like that about you.

266
00:22:31,400 --> 00:22:33,118
Have you ever

267
00:22:33,119 --> 00:22:34,519
had someone worry about you?

268
00:22:37,160 --> 00:22:39,279
My dream since I was a kid

269
00:22:40,200 --> 00:22:41,200
was to take my father

270
00:22:41,880 --> 00:22:44,599
out of this filthy, rotten gutter.

271
00:22:45,599 --> 00:22:46,599
And now,

272
00:22:47,799 --> 00:22:49,000
I want to take you with me.

273
00:22:49,799 --> 00:22:51,319
He Chusan,

274
00:22:51,799 --> 00:22:53,159
I want a place with an ocean view.

275
00:22:53,640 --> 00:22:54,680
You'll have it.

276
00:22:59,920 --> 00:23:00,920
Happy New Year.

277
00:23:02,240 --> 00:23:03,240
He Chusan,

278
00:23:04,799 --> 00:23:05,839
Happy New Year.

279
00:23:06,119 --> 00:23:07,119
Xia Liuyi.

280
00:23:15,200 --> 00:23:16,640
I'm so afraid of losing you.

281
00:23:28,680 --> 00:23:29,680
I...

282
00:23:38,279 --> 00:23:40,759
I should never have fallen for him.

283
00:23:54,240 --> 00:23:55,240
Don't leave me alone.

284
00:23:55,839 --> 00:23:56,839
Don't go.

285
00:23:57,519 --> 00:23:58,920
Don't leave me all alone.

286
00:24:09,240 --> 00:24:10,279
Trust me.

287
00:24:50,519 --> 00:24:52,519
This is your new beginning.

288
00:25:02,759 --> 00:25:03,759
What the hell?

289
00:25:04,519 --> 00:25:05,519
What's going on?

290
00:25:06,240 --> 00:25:07,319
Is this a pyramid scheme?

291
00:25:53,720 --> 00:25:55,240
Get out, get out! Nothing to see here.

292
00:25:55,640 --> 00:25:56,640
Move it!

293
00:25:57,799 --> 00:25:58,799
Let's go.

294
00:26:01,200 --> 00:26:02,200
What's the deal?

295
00:26:02,880 --> 00:26:03,599
Move it, kid.
Don't ask questions.

296
00:26:04,640 --> 00:26:05,760
Don't get in the boss's way.

297
00:27:20,039 --> 00:27:20,359
Don't move!
Freeze!
Don't move!

298
00:27:21,359 --> 00:27:21,920
Freeze!
Don't move!

299
00:27:23,559 --> 00:27:24,559
Freeze!

300
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:31,200
Xia Liuyi,

301
00:27:31,599 --> 00:27:33,599
you're under arrest for attempted murder.

302
00:27:34,119 --> 00:27:35,119
It wasn't him!

303
00:27:37,279 --> 00:27:38,279
Xia Liuyi!

304
00:27:39,559 --> 00:27:40,559
It's okay.

305
00:27:52,480 --> 00:27:54,880
Take care of yourself, kid.

306
00:27:55,799 --> 00:27:56,799
Wait for me to come back.

307
00:29:07,480 --> 00:29:08,480
Thank you.

308
00:29:10,599 --> 00:29:12,519
Someone will be by later
to take your statement.

309
00:29:15,720 --> 00:29:16,720
Xia Liuyi...

310
00:29:20,473 --> 00:29:21,473
what will happen to him?

311
00:29:24,160 --> 00:29:25,240
If he's innocent,

312
00:29:25,480 --> 00:29:26,480
he'll be released.

313
00:29:27,200 --> 00:29:27,559
But if he's...
I believe in him.

314
00:29:39,279 --> 00:29:40,279
He Chusan,

315
00:29:40,519 --> 00:29:41,880
you have a clean record.

316
00:29:42,799 --> 00:29:43,799
Watch yourself.

317
00:29:44,799 --> 00:29:46,720
Don't associate with the wrong people.

318
00:29:47,200 --> 00:29:48,200
I...

319
00:30:04,880 --> 00:30:05,519
Why do you bother with such

320
00:30:05,520 --> 00:30:07,240
thankless work?

321
00:30:08,039 --> 00:30:08,920
Lu Guangming,

322
00:30:09,039 --> 00:30:10,799
you still have the nerve to call me?

323
00:30:11,640 --> 00:30:13,479
You could've killed
three birds with one stone.

324
00:30:13,480 --> 00:30:14,520
Excuse me, let me through.

325
00:30:16,480 --> 00:30:18,880
You could've used the Inspector's case

326
00:30:19,279 --> 00:30:22,279
to take down the two
biggest gangs in Kowloon.

327
00:30:22,799 --> 00:30:25,160
With that kind of achievement,

328
00:30:25,720 --> 00:30:29,480
you'd be the Chief Inspector by now.

329
00:30:31,480 --> 00:30:32,480
And now look at you.

330
00:30:40,039 --> 00:30:41,479
Did I ever say I wanted any of that?

331
00:30:42,119 --> 00:30:42,960
What I want is...

332
00:30:42,961 --> 00:30:44,720
to be a good cop who serves justice, right?

333
00:30:47,640 --> 00:30:48,838
Brother Jiahua, don't worry.

334
00:30:48,839 --> 00:30:49,919
I'll be just like you,

335
00:30:49,920 --> 00:30:52,000
a good cop who fights for what's right.

336
00:30:58,960 --> 00:31:00,200
What a cliché.

337
00:31:00,799 --> 00:31:02,240
How disappointing.

338
00:31:06,160 --> 00:31:07,319
I don't think so.

339
00:31:08,799 --> 00:31:09,799
I bet

340
00:31:11,759 --> 00:31:13,839
Tang Jiaqi taught you that too.

341
00:31:23,559 --> 00:31:24,559
Mr. Xie,

342
00:31:27,279 --> 00:31:28,519
you're so useless,

343
00:31:29,559 --> 00:31:31,279
you can't get anything done.

344
00:31:33,160 --> 00:31:34,240
But five years ago,

345
00:31:36,119 --> 00:31:38,920
when the gangs and the cops killed Jiaqi,

346
00:31:40,799 --> 00:31:41,880
his body

347
