348
00:31:46,759 --> 00:31:47,919
Do you think he regretted it?

349
00:31:49,200 --> 00:31:50,200
Regret?

350
00:31:50,799 --> 00:31:51,680
He was just

351
00:31:51,681 --> 00:31:54,559
a stupid cop who only cared about justice.

352
00:32:03,240 --> 00:32:04,799
That "stupid cop"

353
