was my brother.

354
00:32:34,400 --> 00:32:36,119
I'm not as noble as you.

355
00:32:36,799 --> 00:32:38,480
I know his death was a setup,

356
00:32:39,559 --> 00:32:41,559
but you still want to talk about evidence.

357
00:32:43,157 --> 00:32:44,680
I only know an eye for an eye.

358
00:32:47,680 --> 00:32:49,720
Anyone involved in my brother's death,

359
00:32:50,759 --> 00:32:52,680
I don't care what it takes,

360
00:32:53,839 --> 00:32:55,318
I'll make sure they feel

361
00:32:55,319 --> 00:32:57,480
exactly what true agony is.

362
00:34:09,760 --> 00:34:10,760
You idiot.

363
00:35:14,320 --> 00:35:15,639
Can I come in for a bit?

364
00:35:17,320 --> 00:35:18,320
Officer Lu.

365
00:35:49,039 --> 00:35:49,760
No way.

366
00:35:49,880 --> 00:35:50,880
Is that it?

367
00:35:51,000 --> 00:35:51,639
Let me go!
Ignore him.

368
00:35:52,401 --> 00:35:53,760
Don't let it blow you up!

369
00:35:54,159 --> 00:35:55,000
Let's be friends!
I'm serious!

370
00:35:55,640 --> 00:35:56,679
Let's be friends!

371
00:35:59,599 --> 00:36:00,960
Don't leave me alone!

372
00:36:01,280 --> 00:36:02,280
Don't go!

373
00:36:03,400 --> 00:36:04,440
It's going to blow!

374
00:36:05,119 --> 00:36:06,159
Don't go!

375
00:36:07,519 --> 00:36:09,079
Tell us how to make money.

376
00:36:10,159 --> 00:36:11,239
As the saying goes,

377
00:36:11,440 --> 00:36:13,239
the key to investing is the three Rs.

378
00:36:13,559 --> 00:36:14,840
Do you know what they are?

379
00:36:15,480 --> 00:36:15,920
Returns,
Risks,

380
00:36:17,159 --> 00:36:18,159
and Relative Value.

381
00:36:18,360 --> 00:36:19,840
Returns, Risks, and Relative Value.

382
00:36:20,039 --> 00:36:21,039
Got it?

383
00:36:23,039 --> 00:36:24,760
As their financial advisor,

384
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:26,880
I make them over three million a month.

385
00:36:27,400 --> 00:36:28,719
Three million!

386
00:36:29,199 --> 00:36:31,559
A stack of cash higher than this ceiling!

387
00:36:31,760 --> 00:36:34,559
Three million!

388
00:36:34,880 --> 00:36:36,440
Today we sleep on the floor,

389
00:36:37,079 --> 00:36:38,960
