390
00:36:39,320 --> 00:36:41,880
Be the boss!

391
00:36:41,960 --> 00:36:43,479
Follow me and you'll make millions!

392
00:36:43,480 --> 00:36:44,759
Do you believe in yourselves?

393
00:36:44,760 --> 00:36:47,239
Yes!

394
00:36:47,519 --> 00:36:48,199
Today

395
00:36:48,200 --> 00:36:49,479
is your

396
00:36:49,480 --> 00:36:50,480
new beginning!

397
00:37:03,960 --> 00:37:04,960
Brother Liuyi.
